message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_NAME_EXISTS
message.locale: A questionnaire with this Name already exists.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_STATUS_RELEASED
message.locale: This questionnaire has been released and cannot be modified. To modify the questionnaire a new In Edit version must be created.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_DELETE_STATUS_RELEASED
message.locale: This questionnaire has been released and cannot be deleted.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_NEW_VERSION_STATUS_INEDIT
message.locale: There is currently an In Edit version of this questionnaire. This must be released or deleted before a new version can be created.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_RELEASE_FOR_RELEASED_QUESTIONNAIRE
message.locale: This questionnaire version has already been released. To release a new version an In Edit version must be created.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_RELEASE_QUESTIONNAIRE_TP_INEDIT
message.locale: This questionnaire Version cannot be released as there is an In Edit typical picture associated with it. The associated In Edit typical picture must be released or deleted before this questionnaire version can be released.

message.name: ERR_REMOVE_TP_FOR_INEDIT_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION
message.locale: This questionnaire has been released and cannot be modified. To remove the typical picture a new In Edit version of the questionnaire must be created.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_ENT_RELEASED_SYNC
message.locale: This questionnaire has been released and therefore associated typical pictures cannot be synchronized.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_XRV_SYNC_NO_TP
message.locale: This questionnaire has no typical pictures and cannot be synchronized.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_STATUS_RELEASED_QUESTIONS_EDIT
message.locale: This version has been released and cannot be modified. To modify the questionnaire you must first create a new In Edit version.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_ASSOCIATED_TO_RELEASED_DETERMINATIONPACKAGE
message.locale: There is a released version of a Determination Package which includes this script. Changing the script will have implications for Change of Circumstances and Clone functions; the previous answers cannot be pre-populated due to this change in the script.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_DELETE_STATUS_RELEASED_AND_ASSOCIATED_TO_DETERMINATIONPACKAGE
message.locale: This questionnaire is released and associated to a determination package and therefore cannot be deleted.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_DELETE_QUESTION_GROUP_ASSOCIATED_TO_OTHER_SCRIPTS
message.locale: This question script contains question groups which are used by other question scripts, it cannot be deleted.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_DELETE_NOT_LATEST_VERSION
message.locale: This is not the latest questionnaire version, it cannot be deleted.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_FV_RELEASE_QUESTIONNAIRE_VERSION_ASSOCIATED_TO_INEDIT_QUESTIONNAIRE
message.locale: This questionnaire version has links to another 'In Edit' questionnaire version. That questionnaire version must be released before releasing this questionnaire version.

message.name: ERR_QUESTIONNAIREVERSION_ASSOCIATED_TO_RELEASED_QUESTIONNAIRE
message.locale: This questionnaire is linked to other released questionnaires. If you wish these other questionnaires to use the new version of this questionnaire, they should be updated to refer to this new questionnaire version.
